                Last update 07:35 | 11/01/2017</div><div style="float:right;"><span class="fmsidWidgetLike" data-type="article" data-webcode="English" data-key="english.vietnamnet.vn_english-education_170595" data-guid="" data-id="170595" data-title="Problems in education sector mount" data-url="http://english.vietnamnet.vn/fms/education/170595/problems-in-education-sector-mount.html" data-thumb="http://img.cdn2.vietnamnet.vn/Images/english/2017/01/03/21/20170103215351-edu-problem.jpg"> </span><span class="fmsidWidgetRating" data-max="5" data-current="0" data-type="article" data-webcode="English" data-key="english.vietnamnet.vn_english-education_170595" data-guid="" data-id="170595" data-title="Problems in education sector mount" data-url="http://english.vietnamnet.vn/fms/education/170595/problems-in-education-sector-mount.html" data-thumb="http://img.cdn2.vietnamnet.vn/Images/english/2017/01/03/21/20170103215351-edu-problem.jpg"> </span></div><div class="content-share"><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="javascript:$vnn.Utilities.FacebookShare();" class="fl_l"><span class="hidden">Facebook</span></a><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="javascript:$vnn.Utilities.TwitterShare();" class="fl_l"><span class="hidden">Twitter</span></a><div class="fl_l"><a href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?v=250&amp;username=xa-4cae93db4d7923db" class="addthis_button_compact"><span class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style hidden">addthis_button_compact</span></a></div><a id="cmdSendEmail" title="Send to friend" class="mail" href="javascript:void(0);"><span class="hidden">Send Email</span></a><a class="print" href="javascript:$vnn.Utilities.PrintEle('#articlePrintArea');" id="articlePrintButton"><span class="hidden">Printer</span></a><br class="clear" /></div><br class="clear" /></div><script language="javascript">
